<h1 class="page-title">Arthem</h1>

<p>Arthem started as an idea to solve a personal problem of mine long ago. I'd applied to a job in web design during college and aced the interview, but the person doing the hiring was away, so all that was left to assess me in the end were my credentials on paper.</p>

<p>I realised that I ought to just go my own way, and I started this little company with a friend of mine with the goal of building niche websites for creative types in Montreal. I registered the company and we got to buisness.</p>

